    "Furthermore, our empirical study lacks a theoretical understanding of suffix transfer learning, which warrants further investigation.",
    "Our study does not propose a new attack paradigm to jailbreak LLMs.",
    "Instead, we investigate the existing adversarial suffix-based jailbreak attack, aiming to understand the properties of adversarial suffixes in a better way.",
    "For example, we mainly examine the suffix transferability with suffix search efficiency.",
    "This further understanding of suffix transferability can help guide the design of more effective defense methods in the future."
